No fewer than 18 people in the back of a bakkie were injured when the vehicle overturned on Saturday in Vanderbijlpark Gauteng.The driver lost control in Delfos Boulevard according to ER24. He and his passengers were taken to hospital.In Cape Town two pedestrians were killed when a car overturned on the N1 and hit them on the central median near the Durban Road intersection in Bellville.City of Cape Town spokeswoman Maxine Bezuidenhout said the accident left another pedestrian seriously injured. TMG Digital 